---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
description: Weekly reflections from Sit Raleigh, expanding on each week's teaching, guided by Cary Keishin Brief.
---

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <p class="page-eyebrow">Weekly reflections</p>
    <div class="blog-hero-row">
      <h1 class="page-headline">Blog</h1>
      <img src="/images/sit-raleigh-logo.png" alt="" class="blog-hero-logo" />
    </div>
    <p class="page-sub">Each week, we expand on the teaching from our newsletter &mdash; a place to sit with the ideas a little longer.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="section section--parchment">
  <div class="section-inner">
    {% set posts = collections.blog | sortByDate | reverse %}
    {% if posts.length %}
    <div class="blog-grid">
      {% for post in posts %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="blog-card">
        {% if post.data.featured_image %}
        <div class="blog-card-img" style="background-image:url('{{ post.data.featured_image }}');"></div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="blog-card-body">
          <div class="blog-card-date">{{ post.data.date | shortDate }}{% if post.data.author %} &middot; {{ post.data.author }}{% endif %}</div>
          <h2 class="blog-card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
          {% if post.data.summary %}<p class="blog-card-summary">{{ post.data.summary }}</p>{% endif %}
          <span class="blog-card-more">Read &rarr;</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <p style="text-align:center;color:var(--umber-lt);">No posts yet &mdash; check back soon.</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
